### GET alle Brands
GET http://localhost:8080/api/brands

### GET eine Brand byId 2
GET http://localhost:8080/api/brands/2

### POST neue Brand anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/brands
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Müller", "countries": "Deutschland" }

### PUT neue Brand direkt mal updaten
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/brands/5
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Müller Milch", "countries": "Deutschland" }

### DELETE Brand
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/brands/4


### GET alle Produkte
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### GET für Produkte filtern nach Brand
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products?brandId=2

### GET ein Produkt byId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### POST neues Produkt anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "1234567890",
  "name": "Joghurt natur",
  "brandId": 2,
  "caloriesKcal": 65,
  "protein": 4.5,
  "carbs": 5.2
}


### POST Brand Franziskaner anlegen (Id 6)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/brands
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Franziskaner",
"countries": "Deutschland"
}

### PUT - Produkt 2 (Butter) komplett ersetzen mit Daten aus Open Food Facts
### Quelle: https://world.openfoodfacts.net/api/v2/search?code=4072700802525&fields=product_name,nutriments,brands
### energy-kcal_100g: 21.0 kcal, proteins_100g: 0.6, carbohydrates_100g: 4.4
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "4072700802525",
  "name": "Franziskaner Weissbier Alkoholfrei 0,5 L",
  "brandId": 5,
  "caloriesKcal": 21.0,
  "protein": 0.6,
  "carbs": 4.4
}

### GET - Prüfen, ob das Update geklappt hat
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/2

### DELETE Produkt
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### POST  - neues Frühstück anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Frühstück",
  "name": "Shake mit Kokosmilch",
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "amountGrams": 200.0 }
  ]
}

### GET Kategorie "Snack"
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meals/category?category=snack

### GET Namenssuche unvollständig
GET http://localhost:8080/api/brands/search?name=bau

### GET Suche nach Produkt
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?name=joghurt

### GET Suche alle Produkte, die "Shake" im Namen haben
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meals/search?name=shake

### GET Suche nach einer Mahlzeit-Kategorie
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meals/category?category=Frühstück

### GET extern Data from OpenFoodFacts, nur nachschauen (speichert nichts)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/barcode/4002334113032

### POST extern Data from OpenFoodFacts, in DB importieren (legt Brand + Product an)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/barcode/4063367519994/import

### DELETE sollte 404 mit "Brand with id 999 not found" geben
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/brands/999

### DELETE sollte 204 geben (Meal hat keine Abhängigkeiten)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/meals/1

### DELETE sollte 409 mit "still referenced by products" geben
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/brands/2

### POST Validation-Test Brand (400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/brands
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":  "", "countries": "Deutschland"}

### POST Validation-Test Product (400)
POST localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{"barcode": "12332", "name": "Test", "caloriesKcal": -50,
  "protein": 7.9, "carbs": 0}

### POST Validation-Test Meals (400)
POST localhost:8080/api/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{"category": "Snack", "name": "Leer", "items": []}

### POST Validation-Test Meals (400)
POST localhost:8080/api/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{"category": "Frühstück", "name": "Müsli", "items": [{"amountGrams":  120}]}

### POST Validation-Test Meals (201)
POST localhost:8080/api/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{"category": "Frühstück", "name": "Joghurt", "items": [{"productId": 2, "amountGrams": 135}]}